[SN]TITLE[SN]
John Timpson: 'Mavericks likely to vote to leave EU'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
John Timpson, chair of the chain of cobblers Timpson, and father of Conservative MP and Remain supporter Edward Timpson, plans to vote "leave" in the EU referendum.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
13 May 2016 Last updated at 10:21 BST
As part of BBC Newsnight's My Decision series, he explains the reasoning behind his vote.
